Synopsis: Starts an internal function within a specified module.
Description: This function starts an internal function within a specified module by importing the module and executing the provided script block.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Start-InternalFunction -ScriptBlock { Get-ChildItem } -Module "ExampleModule"
This example starts the internal function 'Get-ChildItem' within the 'ExampleModule' module.
